<HR size="1" color="#12350C">
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
I've searched the DAoC forums far and wide and have yet to find any info regarding this obviously broken spell.  So now i'm posting here to find out if anyone has heard or seen any info regarding the Mentalist Charm spell being broken.  I know that other realms' classes, which use the charm spell, have a working charm spell.  If it is in fact broken and needs to be fixxed, i can live with this and wait patiently.  The thing that is driving me nuts, is that i have had no response from my appeals nor my Email sent to Sanya nor my postings on any and all boards regarding this spell and whether or not it is being worked on and when we might expect to see the fix.  If someone/anyone somewhere would PLEASE tell me what's going on with this spell, i would GREATLY appreciate it and would be forever in your debt.<P>For those that don't know what's happening with the spell, here's a brief description of what happens when u try to use it.  First off you can not use it on any old mob.  The target must be a humanoid type creature.  If u try to cast on anything other then a humanoid type creature, you get a message saying it can not be done. (not in those words of course)  When u find a humanoid creature to cast the charm spell on, it will NOT stay charmed as advertised or really in any other capacity.  As soon as u attempt to target anything other then the charmed mob, the spell breaks and the charmed mob runs away.  If the target is not on the charmed creature at ALL times u can not hold the charm or in other words the spell will break.  And it does so IMMEDIATELY with no time in between to re-charm the creature.  This has been like this since the beginning and any other mentalist u ask about this spell all receive the same exact results.  This entire situation with the charm spell has been disappointing to say the least.  Worst part of it all is the lack of any response on it whatsoever.  A simple acknowledgement will do and maybe a time frame on when or if it's ever going to get fixxed.<P>My humble apologies for posting a rant here, tis not my intent, just want to be able to cast this spell eventually.  I watched a sorcerer use this spell in the Albion realm and it was pretty damn cool.  Overall i love the game just extremely disappointed that my chosen class is missing a key spell!  <IMG SRC="frown.gif" border="0"><P>--------------------<P>Mumrah Dunestorm
</FONT>
